author: Bethesda Softworks
description:
Dive deeper into the Seasons of the Worm Cult storyline, confront sinister threats, and earn new rewards with the Feast of Shadows dungeon pack, featuring two all-new dungeons: Black Gem Foundry and Naj-Caldeesh.

Feast of Shadows is now live on PC/Mac, Steam, and the Epic Games Store, and arrives September 3 on Xbox and PlayStation consoles.

Official Site: https://www.elderscrollsonline.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline
Bluesky: https://bsky.app/profile/elderscrollsonline.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline
Instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence. Online interactions not rated by the ESRB.
